channel.title: HELP! i cant get my server online
channel.description: ive followed many server tuts and think ive done everyting right, ive portforwarded and all the other things u need to start a server, everything seems to be ok but then when i try to log in it says "error connecting to server" ! i need help any1 who can help me solve this will get admin status on my first ever server! btw tht is not a bribe because i actually need staff, thanks for looking

item.title: HELP! i cant get my server online
item.dc:creator: @baselm baselm
item.description:
@baselm wrote:

did u make a no-ip? if u did change the ip to ur no-ip.
how to do that?
go to gui.java, or Egui.java if u didnt have any of them i think at client.java
if u had gui.java search for

serverip

and u will see something like this

Serverip = "XXXXX.no-ip.biz";

change the ip in this code, to ur no-ip
or just put in 127.0.0.1,
if u had egui.java i think u should search for

setserver

and u would see the same, (an ip) change it to urs
same with the client.java
